title: Adversity is Your Friend
itunes:title: Adversity is Your Friend
description:
Episode 309 - Scared of a little adversity? It's good for you, it makes you better. A muscle does not grow unless it is put under intense pressure. The same goes for you, so seek out that adversity and grow in the process.
